Catheter Flush
Text:
1L heparinized saline
Within 72 hours of surgery
Repeat weekly until dialysis begins
Use CAPD exchange guidelines for sterility

Headline: Dressing & Exit-Site Maintenance
Text:
• Do not remove for 7 days after surgery
  • Keep clean, dry and intact
  • Contact dialysis nurse ifdressing becomes soilded or loose
  • Do not shower, bathe or swim
  • Resume showering one month postoperatively
  • Keep sterile gauze dressing over wound as it heals
